instruction: In this task, given a sentence in the English language, your task is to convert it into the Lao (Laotian) language.
input: Missy Elliott’s “Lose Control” featuring Ciara and Fat Man Scoop gained 5-3 while “Don’t Cha” dropped to No. 5.
output: "Lose Control" ຂອງ ມີດຊີ ເອວເລຍຮ່ວມດ້ວຍຊິເອຣາແລະ Fat Man Scoop ໄຕ່ຈາກອັນດັບ 5ມາຍັງອັນດັບ 3 ຂະນະທີ່ "Don't Cha" ຫລົ່ນມາຢູ່ອັນດັບທີ 5.

instruction: In this task, given a sentence in the English language, your task is to convert it into the Lao (Laotian) language.
input: A sixteen-year-old girl, Darlene Etienne, was pulled out from underneath the rubble of a collapsed school in Haiti yesterday, fifteen days after a magnitude 7.0 earthquake struck the country, devastating most buildings in the capital, Port-au-Prince.
output: ໃນມື້ວານນີ້ ເດັກຍິງ ອາຍຸ ສິບຫົກ ປີ ຊື່ວ່າ ນາງ ດາເລັນ ອີຕຽນເນ ໄດ້ຖືກຊ່ວຍດຶງອອກມາຈາກພາຍໃຕ້ເສດຊາກຂອງໂຮງຮຽນທີ່ຖະລົ່ມ ຢູ່ທີ່ ປະເທດໄຮຕິ ພາຍຫຼັງ ສິບຫ້າ ວັນ ທີ່ເກີດແຜນດິນໄຫວລະດັບ 7.0 ແມັກຕີຕູດ ໄດ້ ກະທົບໃສ່ ປະເທດ ແລະ ທຳລາຍຕືກອາຄານເປັນ ສ່ວນ ຫຼວງຫຼາຍ ຢູ່ໃນເມືອງຫຼວງ ພອດໂອພຣິນ.

instruction: In this task, given a sentence in the English language, your task is to convert it into the Lao (Laotian) language.
input: "As a routine matter and out of an abundance of caution, US-CERT issued the situational awareness report to industry stakeholders."

instruction: In this task, given a sentence in the English language, your task is to convert it into the Lao (Laotian) language.
input: A minimum of 85 Hindu pilgrims have been killed in India and 64 injured after their lorry and trailer plunged 24m (80ft) into a river gorge late last night.
output: ມີນັກສະແຫວງບຸນຮິນດູ ຈໍານວນຢ 85 ຄົນ ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍ ເສຍຊີວິດໃນປະເທດອິນເດຍ ແລະ ອີກ 64 ຄົນ ໄດ້ຮັບບາດເຈັບ ພາຍຫຼັງທີ່ລົດບັນທຸກ ແລະ ລົດພ່ວງຂອງພວກເຂົາຕົກລົງໄປໃນນໍ້າປະມານ 24 m(80 ft) ທີ່ຢູ່ລະຫວ່າງຮ່ອມພູ ໃນຄືນຕອນມື້ວານ.
